text: Mumtaz Begum is an Indian politician. She was elected as MLA of Metiaburuz Vidhan Sabha Constituency in 2011 in West Bengal Legislative Assembly.List of Winners in West Bengal 2011 She is an All India Trinamool Congress politician. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:West Bengal MLAs 2011–2016 Category:Women in West Bengal politics Category:Living people
